import React from 'react';
import Card from './Cards';

function App(){
    return(
        <>
            <Card 
                imgSrc = "https://picsum.photos/200/300"
                title = "A Netflix Original Series"
                Sname = "DARK"
                link = "https://picsum.photos/"
            />
            <Card 
                imgSrc = "https://picsum.photos/200/300"
                title = "A Netflix Original Series"
                Sname = "Extra Curricular"
                link = "https://picsum.photos/"
            />
            <Card 
                imgSrc = "https://picsum.photos/200/300"
                title = "A Netflix Original Series"
                Sname = "Stranger Things"
                link = "https://picsum.photos/"
            />
        </>
    );
}

export default App;
